# Names here, values in .env — .env is gitignored and this file is committed.
# Each integration's key gets one line, added when it goes live
# (os/playbooks/add-integration.md). The value goes in .env and in the owner's
# password manager; it never appears in any tracked file or in chat.

# Example — replace with a real key name when your first integration goes live:
EXAMPLE_API_KEY=
